messages.content: What is the purpose of ComfyUI-CUP?
ComfyUI-CUP is a bridge for ComfyUI-BlenderAI-node that provides thumbnail service, allows specifying InputImage/SaveImage nodes, and offers node-diff/queue service.
ComfyUI-CUP depends on ComfyUI-Studio for its thumbnail service.
To install ComfyUI-CUP, navigate to the 'ComfyUI/custom_nodes' directory and run the command: git clone https://github.com/AIGODLIKE/ComfyUI-CUP.git.
Is ComfyUI-CUP compatible with other nodes or plugins?
ComfyUI-CUP is specifically designed for use with ComfyUI-BlenderAI-node and may not be compatible with other nodes or plugins.
Does ComfyUI-CUP provide nodes for web-end?
No, ComfyUI-CUP does not provide any nodes for web-end functionality.
What services does ComfyUI-CUP offer for ComfyUI-BlenderAI-node?
ComfyUI-CUP offers thumbnail service (dependent on ComfyUI-Studio), allows specifying InputImage/SaveImage nodes, and provides node-diff/queue service for ComfyUI-BlenderAI-node.
Is ComfyUI-CUP an independent plugin or an extension for ComfyUI-BlenderAI-node?

ComfyUI-CUP is an extension specifically designed for ComfyUI-BlenderAI-node, enhancing its functionality by providing additional services such as thumbnail service, node specification, and node-diff/queue service.
